prodNameC: 常盈甲型胎蛋白放射免疫檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1. Anti-AFP monoclonal antibody-coated tubes.
2. Monoclonal 125I-labelled anti-AFP tracer antibody:
The vial contains 320 kBq at the date of manufacture of 125I-labelled immunoglobulin in buffer containing bovine serum albumin, sodium azide (<0.1%) and a dye.
3. AFP calibrators:
  The calibrator vials contain from 0 to 400 IU/ mL AFP in bovine serum with sodium azide (<0.1%)
4. Control samples:
  The vials contain AFP in lyophilised human serum.
5. Phosphate buffer:
  The vial contains buffer with bovine serum albumin.
6. Wash solution (20x)
applicantName: 常盈實業股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市北投區永興路一段49號
efficacy: 利用放射性體外免疫方法定量血清或羊水中AFP濃度。
